@startuml
' 样式配置
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #f0f8ff
    BorderColor #aabbcc
    FontColor black
}
skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #f9f9f9
    BorderColor #333333
}

' 划分区域：用户态 / 内核态
box "【用户态 User Space】" #LightYellow
actor User
end box

box "【内核态 Kernel Space | VFS + 文件系统层】" #LightCyan
participant VFS
participant "Parent Inode\n(父目录test)" as ParentInode
participant "Super Block\n(ext4超级块)" as SuperBlock
participant "New Dentry\n(a.txt)" as Dentry
participant "New Inode\n(文件inode)" as Inode
participant "File Struct\n(打开文件句柄)" as File
end box

database "Disk 磁盘硬件" as Disk

' 时序步骤+红色编号注释
User -> VFS: <color:red>1</color> open("test/a.txt",O_CREAT,0644)【陷入系统调用，从用户态切内核态】
activate VFS

VFS -> VFS: <color:red>2</color> 路径拆分解析：/ → test → a.txt
VFS -> ParentInode: lookup查找父目录inode
activate ParentInode
note right: 调用inode_operations->lookup，dcache查询目录项
VFS <-- ParentInode: 返回父inode+所属super_block指针
deactivate ParentInode

VFS -> Dentry: <color:red>3</color> d_alloc()新建空dentry
activate Dentry
note left: d_name="a.txt", d_inode=NULL【负dentry占位】
VFS <-- Dentry: 空dentry返回

VFS -> SuperBlock: <color:red>4</color> 从超级块分配空闲inode编号
activate SuperBlock
note right: 依赖super_operations->alloc_inode，sb管理全局空闲inode
SuperBlock -> Disk: 在磁盘inode区分配磁盘inode物理位置
VFS <-- SuperBlock: 拿到inode号
deactivate SuperBlock

VFS -> Inode: <color:red>5</color> 初始化内存struct inode
activate Inode
note right: i_nlink=1、i_sb指向超级块、绑定ext4 file_operations
VFS <-- Inode: 有效inode构造完成

VFS -> Dentry: <color:red>6</color> d_instantiate(dentry,inode)绑定
Dentry -> Inode: d_inode = &inode 建立指针关联
note left: dentry与inode正式关联，文件名→文件本体打通

VFS -> ParentInode: <color:red>7</color> 父目录inode追加目录记录(a.txt+ino)
ParentInode -> Disk: 写入父目录磁盘数据区，更新父inode属性
deactivate Inode

VFS -> File: <color:red>8</color> 分配struct file打开实例
activate File
note right: f_dentry/f_inode挂载指针、f_pos=0读写偏移置零
VFS <-- File: file构造完毕

VFS -> User: <color:red>9</color> 分配fd，返回文件描述符【切回用户态】
deactivate File
deactivate Dentry
deactivate VFS
@enduml